  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/86d788322d497b16bde068912a232c81.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/86d788322d497b16bde068912a232c81.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on an Epic Adventure!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare your gear and decide: will you face this challenge alone or alongside your friends? The choice is yours, but the journey promises excitement and danger at every turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=608 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.mp4?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Path</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Warrior, Archer, or Mage and vanquish the monsters that try to stop you. Each class offers unique abilities and playstyles, so choose the one that best suits you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/9a0be8697bd5c8487badc024a175e264.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/9a0be8697bd5c8487badc024a175e264.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Evolve and Improve</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience during battles and unlock powerful upgrades in your talent tree. Visit the blacksmith to strengthen your equipment. The possibilities for growth are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leave Your Mark</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feats won’t go unnoticed! Compete for glory and compare your performance with other brave adventurers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/069cb6f2750e16a5b1af5bcdce5bb8de.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/069cb6f2750e16a5b1af5bcdce5bb8de.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join the Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t miss this opportunity! Add the game to your wish list and follow our weekly updates, filled with new challenges, features, and surprises. The journey is just beginning, and we can’t wait to see where it takes you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/86d788322d497b16bde068912a232c81.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/86d788322d497b16bde068912a232c81.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on an Epic Adventure!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare your gear and decide: will you face this challenge alone or alongside your friends? The choice is yours, but the journey promises excitement and danger at every turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=608 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.mp4?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Path</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Warrior, Archer, or Mage and vanquish the monsters that try to stop you. Each class offers unique abilities and playstyles, so choose the one that best suits you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/9a0be8697bd5c8487badc024a175e264.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/9a0be8697bd5c8487badc024a175e264.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Evolve and Improve</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience during battles and unlock powerful upgrades in your talent tree. Visit the blacksmith to strengthen your equipment. The possibilities for growth are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leave Your Mark</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feats won’t go unnoticed! Compete for glory and compare your performance with other brave adventurers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/069cb6f2750e16a5b1af5bcdce5bb8de.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/069cb6f2750e16a5b1af5bcdce5bb8de.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join the Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t miss this opportunity! Add the game to your wish list and follow our weekly updates, filled with new challenges, features, and surprises. The journey is just beginning, and we can’t wait to see where it takes you!</p>",
